{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":null,"text":"好大的风，好冷，真该多穿两件衣服的。","tone":"调侃","chapter":125,"line_start":4,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"你难道已觉得有些受不了么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":125,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"大伯你放心，我身子还没有那么娇嫩。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"一个内功已有火候的人，虽不能说可以完全寒暑不侵，但至少总不该像常人那么畏寒畏暑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"你所练的武功，乃是无数位武林前辈的心血结晶，可说无一招不是武学中的精萃，而且你小时万大叔就已替你打了很多的底子，并没有让你功夫走入邪路，这种种条件加在一起，所以我才放心让你和花无缺动手。但你功力究竟如何，我并不知道，你很聪明，也很幸运，我惟一只怕你性情太浮，心思太躁，没有将功夫练纯。","tone":"认真","chapter":125,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"我做别的事虽三心二意，但练武时倒很专心的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":125,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"但愿如此就好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"你既已和花无缺交过手，可知他的武功如何？","tone":"疑问","chapter":125,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"移花宫能够享这么大的名，武功实在有独得之秘，尤其那种'移花接玉'的功夫，实在令人头痛。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"幸好我多少已摸出其中一些诀窍了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":125,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"移花接玉只不过是移花宫许多武功之一，移花宫的武功变化繁复，虽冷静却极深契，而且，我看花无缺外表看来虽不如你聪明，其实绝不会比你笨，你的武功博而杂，他的武功精而深，你和他动手时，切莫要和他以招式硬拼，最好先想法子将他的功力耗去几成。","tone":"严肃","chapter":125,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"这我也知道，他的根基实在比我打得好。我和他交手，胜算并不多，但我却占了一个很大的便宜。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":32,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"武学之道，绝没有便宜可占，你想占人便宜，你就先败了。","tone":"厉声","chapter":125,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"是，只不过……他武功的深浅，我已全知道，我武功的路数，他却一点也不知道，因为我从来未将真实的武功在人前炫露过。","tone":"认真","chapter":125,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"很好，知己知彼，方能百战百胜。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":125,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"燕大伯，我也想问问你老人家一件事。","tone":"好奇","chapter":125,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_yan_nan_tian","speaker_name":"燕南天","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"你说吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_yan_nan_tian","text":"你老人家若真和邀月宫主动起手来，能有几分胜算，几成把握？","tone":"好奇","chapter":125,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_wan_chun_liu","speaker_name":"万春流","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"时候已快到了，你准备好了么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_wan_chun_liu","text":"我也还有件事想问万大叔。","tone":"认真","chapter":125,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_wan_chun_liu","speaker_name":"万春流","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"你问的话我并不见得全能回答的，我知道的事并不比你多。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":125,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_wan_chun_liu","text":"但这件事万大叔一定知道。","tone":"微笑","chapter":125,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_wan_chun_liu","text":"无论酒中是否有毒，万大叔现在都莫要告诉我。","tone":"认真","chapter":125,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_wan_chun_liu","speaker_name":"万春流","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"这又是为了什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":125,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_xiao_yu_er","speaker_name":"小鱼儿","listener":"char_wan_chun_liu","text":"因为酒中若真有毒，我就会很生气，酒中若是无毒，我又会觉得很难受，所以万大叔还是等我打完了再告诉我，免得我分心。","tone":"无奈","chapter":125,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_wan_chun_liu","speaker_name":"万春流","listener":"char_xiao_yu_er","text":"好，反正你这孩子做的事，总是叫人猜不透的。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":125,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_mu_rong_shuang","speaker_name":"慕容双","listener":null,"text":"你看见了吗？小鱼儿和燕大侠像是有说不完的话要说，但花无缺和移花宫主只是站在那里干瞪眼。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_mu_rong_shan_shan","speaker_name":"慕容珊珊","listener":null,"text":"不错，看来移花宫主对花无缺这一战的胜负根本一点也不关心，他们师徒间难道连一点感情都没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":125,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_liu","speaker_name":"南宫柳","listener":null,"text":"这也许是因为她们觉得花无缺这一战有必胜的把握。","tone":"无奈","chapter":125,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_mu_rong_shan_shan","speaker_name":"慕容珊珊","listener":null,"text":"我看倒未必，花无缺虽然机智武功都不错，但小鱼儿可也不是好惹的，若论动起手来的应变功夫，我看简直没有任何人能比得上他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_mu_rong_shuang","speaker_name":"慕容双","listener":null,"text":"不错，我看花无缺的功力要稍强些，但高手相争，光是功力高并没有太大的作用，主要还是得看当时临机应变，制敌机先。","tone":"陈述","chapter":125,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_qin_jian","speaker_name":"秦剑","listener":null,"text":"据我所知，小鱼儿武学极博，似乎身兼数家之长，这一战至少可有六成胜算。","tone":"认真","chapter":125,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_mu_rong_shan_shan","speaker_name":"慕容珊珊","listener":null,"text":"我看还不止六成。","tone":"得意","chapter":125,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_xiao_nu_shi","speaker_name":"萧女史","listener":"char_tie_zhan","text":"你看你女婿这一战有几成把握？","tone":"疑问","chapter":125,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_tie_zhan","speaker_name":"铁战","listener":"char_xiao_nu_shi","text":"十成。","tone":"得意","chapter":125,"line_start":100,"line_end":100}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiao_yu_er","name":"小鱼儿","alias":[],"identity":"江枫之子，邀月宫主养子","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"江枫与花月奴的孪生子之一，机智狡黠的少年高手","personality":{"traits":["机智","狡黠","乐观","玩世不恭","重情义"],"speech_style":"轻佻幽默，善用反讽","temperament":"外放洒脱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_hua_wu_que","type":"宿敌","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"亦敌亦友的孪生兄弟"},{"target":"char_yan_nan_tian","type":"师徒","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"敬重依赖"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[125],"source_refs":[{"chapter":125,"line_start":4,"line_end":4,"text":"小鱼儿缩了缩脖子"}]},{"id":"char_yan_nan_tian","name":"燕南天","alias":[],"identity":"天下第一神剑","faction":"无","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"江湖公认的天下第一神剑，小鱼儿的义伯父","personality":{"traits":["刚毅","正直","豪迈","深谋远虑","严厉"],"speech_style":"威严稳重，语带训诫","temperament":"沉稳刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_yu_er","type":"师徒","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"指导爱护"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[125],"source_refs":[{"chapter":125,"line_start":6,"line_end":6,"text":"燕南天皱了皱眉"}]},{"id":"char_wan_chun_liu","name":"万春流","alias":[],"identity":"隐居恶人谷的医者","faction":"无","role":"companion","archetype":"healer","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"恶人谷中的医者，曾抚养小鱼儿长大","personality":{"traits":["慈祥","稳重","深藏不露","关爱后辈","谨慎"],"speech_style":"温和慈祥，语带关切","temperament":"沉稳内敛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_yu_er","type":"师徒","intensity":60,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"抚养教导"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[125],"source_refs":[{"chapter"